Executive Profile
Ray   Boegner  Vice President of Business Development, SilverTech, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 1 different industries.----
Background

		Ray Boegner, Greg serves as Vice President of Business Development of SilverTech, Inc. Mr. Boegner is responsible for identifying and acquiring content for the eKIDS Internet representing SilverTech at various trade shows and conferences, as well as leading the marketing, advertising, and public relations efforts and business affairs. Prior to SilverTech, Mr. Boegner served as executive director of program acquisitions for both Twentieth Century Fox Home Entertainment ... and CBS/Fox Home Video where he was responsible for theatrical, children's and special interest programming. He served as director of non-theatrical programming of Warner Home Video where he oversaw the production of successful series and fitness videos, and also served as director of acquisitions for Pacific Arts, PBS Home Video and The Family Channel Home Video labels. Additionally, Mr. Boegner served as a media producer for NASA at the Johnson Space Center in Houston, where he oversaw all live shuttle downlink coverage and produced the media coverage documenting the tragic events following the Challenger explosion. Read Full Background




