Ray F. Boegner



Mr. Ray F. Boegner is President-Cinema Business at Ballantyne Strong, Inc.
Mr. Boegner was previously employed as Vice President-Marketing by Cinema Film Systems.
He received his undergraduate degree from Citrus College and an undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California.



